</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_212" id="105v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_212_r1l1"><expan>De<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd vrteilern auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l2"><expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Lantſchrann cʒü Hirſperg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_212_r1l4"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_212_r1l3">her </ab></add> <expan>Lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd vrteıler / Von der klag <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l5">Margret Drotſmidin tüt von Hanſen veyrabent </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l6"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd vvir Jr eins <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l7"><expan>geholffe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ob er anheim <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wer / Laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l8">wir ew wiſſen / daʒ derſelb vnſer <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> cʒü dıſen <expan>cʒeıt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l9">nicht anheim ıſt / vnd wer er hie heim <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſo <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l10">wir Jr <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> rechtens <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Jm <expan>geholffe<ex>n</ex></expan> / als ſie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ein</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l11">geweıſet ıſt / . vnd wenn er her heim kümt / ſo <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r1l12">wir Jr des <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Jm noch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_212" id="105v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>De<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan> und urteilern auf
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> lantschrann czü Hirsperg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>her</add>
<expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan> und urteiler, von der klag
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, als Margret Drotsmidin tüt von Hansen
                        Veyrabent, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> und wir ir
                        eins <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> im <expan>geholffe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, ob er anheim <expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wer; lassen wir ew wissen, daz derselb unser <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
                        czü disen <expan>czeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> nicht anheim ist und wer er hie
                        heim <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>, so <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        ir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> rechtens <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> im
                                <expan>geholffe<ex>n</ex></expan>, als sie
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ein</expan> geweiset ist. Und wenn er her heim kümt, so
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ir des
                            <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> im noch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen
                                <expan>ungeu<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
